ai.github.io/Austen/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" style=\"text-decoration:none;color:#CF512B !important\"><span style=\"color:#CF512B !important\">TechCrunch AI</span></a>                        </p>                      </td>                    </tr>                    <tr>                      <td colspan=\"2\" style=\"padding-top:10px\">                        <p class=\"em-text-indigo\" style=\"margin:0;font-size:14px;font-family:Geist,Arial,sans-serif;line-height:1.6;color:#41488A !important\">                          <a href=\"https://ironbridge-ai.github.io/Austen/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" style=\"text-decoration:none;display:block;color:#41488A !important\"><span style=\"color:#41488A !important\">Microsoft has created a dedicated AI deployment group backed by $2.5 billion, joining Amazon, OpenAI, and Anthropic in building out professional services specifically to help enterprises adopt AI at scale.</span></a>                        </p>                      </td>                    </tr>                  </table>                </td>              </tr>            </table>          </td>        </tr>        <tr>          <td style=\"padding:0 0 12px 0\">            <table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" border=\"0\"                   style=\"background:#ffffff !important;border-radius:8px;border:1px solid #C2CCD5;border-left:3px solid #CF512B\">              <tr>                <td class=\"em-bg-white\" style=\"padding:20px 22px;background:#ffffff !important\" bgcolor=\"#ffffff\">                  <table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" border=\"0\" width=\"100%\">                    <tr>                      <td width=\"48\" valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:0 14px 0 0\">                        <table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" border=\"0\">                          <tr><td width=\"36\" height=\"36\" align=\"center\" bgcolor=\"#CF512B\" class=\"em-bg-orange\"                                  style=\"width:36p